Package com.intellij.openapi.editor.impl.view

Class VisualLinesIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.openapi.editor.impl.view.VisualLinesIterator

  • public class VisualLinesIterator
extends java.lang.Object
    If one needs to perform some actions for a continuous range of visual lines, using this class would be most surely faster than calculating various values (e.g. start/end offsets) for all visual lines in the range individually.
